== 16S核糖体数据库 ==
因为它存在于大多数微生物并显示适当的变化，16S rRNA基因被用作分类鉴定微生物的标准。大多数细菌和古细菌的16S rRNA基因序列型菌株可在公共数据库得到，例如NCBI数据库。然而，在这些数据库中发现的序列的质量往往没有验证。因此，只收集16S rRNA序列辅助数据库被广泛使用。最经常使用的数据库如下：

1： {{link-en|EzTaxon|EzTaxon Database}}-e. https://web.archive.org/web/20130928154318/http://eztaxon-e.ezbiocloud.net/ <ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Chun | first1 = J. | last2 = Lee | first2 = J.-H. | last3 = Jung | first3 = Y. | last4 = Kim | first4 = M. | last5 = Kim | first5 = S. | last6 = Kim | first6 = B. K. | last7 = Lim | first7 = Y. W. | year = 2007 | title = [[EzTaxon_Database|EzTaxon]]: a web-based tool for the identification of prokaryotes based on 16S ribosomal RNA gene sequences | url = | journal = Int J Syst Evol Microbiol | volume = 57 | issue = | pages = 2259–2261 | doi=10.1099/ijs.0.64915-0}}</ref>

2：核糖体数据库项目。http://rdp.cme.msu.edu/{{Wayback|url=http://rdp.cme.msu.edu/ |date=20200819061707 }} 核糖体数据库项目(RDP)。

3： SILVA. <ref>Elmar Pruesse, Christian Quast, Katrin Knittel, Bernhard M. Fuchs, Wolfgang Ludwig, Jörg Peplies, Frank Oliver Glöckner (2007) Nucleic Acids Res. SILVA: a comprehensive online resource for quality checked and aligned ribosomal RNA sequence data compatible with ARB. December; 35(21): 7188–7196.</ref>

4： Greengenes. Greengenes是基于新生系统发生，提供了标准的操作分类单元集的质量控制，全面的16S参考数据库和分类。该网站的官方主页是http://greengenes.secondgenome.com，并在Creative{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }} Commons许可BY-SA3.0许可<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = DeSantis | first1 = T. Z. | last2 = Hugenholtz | first2 = P. | last3 = Larsen | first3 = N. | last4 = Rojas | first4 = M. | last5 = Brodie | first5 = E. L. | last6 = Keller | first6 = K. | last7 = Huber | first7 = T. | last8 = Dalevi | first8 = D. | last9 = Hu | first9 = P. | last10 = Andersen | first10 = G. L. | year = 2006 | title = Greengenes, a Chimera-Checked 16S rRNA Gene Database and Workbench Compatible with ARB | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_applied-and-environmental-microbiology_2006-07_72_7/page/5069| journal = Appl Environ Microbiol | volume = 72 | issue = | pages = 5069–72 | doi=10.1128/aem.03006-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = McDonald | first1 = D | last2 = Price | first2 = MN | last3 = Goodrich | first3 = J | last4 = Nawrocki | first4 = EP | last5 = DeSantis | first5 = TZ | last6 = Probst | first6 = A | last7 = Andersen | first7 = GL | last8 = Knight | first8 = R | last9 = Hugenholtz | first9 = P | year = 2011 | title = An improved Greengenes taxonomy with explicit ranks for ecological and evolutionary analyses of bacteria and archaea | url = | journal = ISME | volume = 6 | issue = | pages = 610–618 | doi = 10.1038/ismej.2011.139 }}</ref>。

